*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Include          ZMMR0031_O01
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Module CREATE_ALV_0100 OUTPUT
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
MODULE CREATE_ALV_0100 OUTPUT.

  IF GO_GRID IS NOT BOUND.

    PERFORM SET_GRID.
    PERFORM SET_FCAT.
    PERFORM SET_LAYO.
    PERFORM SET_SORT.
    PERFORM SET_FUNC.
    PERFORM DISPLAY_ALV.

    ELSE.

      PERFORM REFRESH_GRID.

  ENDIF.
ENDMODULE.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Module STATUS_0100 OUTPUT
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
MODULE STATUS_0100 OUTPUT.
 SET PF-STATUS 'S100'.
 SET TITLEBAR 'T100'.
ENDMODULE.